      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLESSED RAIN (8) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Faded to finish fourth over 410m at Horsham (23.86) in a Mix 3/4 but is better placed coming back in trip. Has never missed the frame here at the trip from three starts. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Worth another chance. NAUGHTY NORM (1) finished in the minors last start over the 390m at this track but ran a strong 22.17 last start. Harder here but expected to measure up. PAW MISSY (6) was a strong course and distance winner last time, claiming a Grade 5 in a quick 22.16 and a new PB here. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. PAW XENA (3) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
